  "keyFeatures": [
    "Proof-of-Antiquity consensus — older hardware earns higher multipliers (up to 4x for mythic-era CPUs)",
    "AI-powered hardware fingerprinting with 6 checks (clock skew, cache timing, SIMD identity, thermal entropy, instruction jitter, anti-emulation)",
    "15+ supported CPU architectures including PowerPC, SPARC, MIPS, 68K, RISC-V, Cell BE",
    "RTC token with Solana bridge (wRTC) for DeFi interoperability",
    "Agent Economy SDK (RIP-302) for AI-agent micropayments and machine-to-machine transfers",
    "BoTTube — AI-native video platform powered by RustChain agents",
    "Blockchain-Certified Open Source (BCOS) verification system",
    "Time-based loyalty multipliers — hardware value grows as it ages",
    "E-waste prevention — 250 kg diverted per fleet, ~1,300 kg CO2 avoided",
    "Testnet faucet for developers building on RustChain"
  ],
